data.description: This Adorable Home in Fort Worth awaits you! Walk across the street to the elementary school! This home offers Stone accents, 10 ft. ceilings, lots of cabinets, SS appliances, a Covered Back Patio, and a full Sprinkler System in the front and back yard. This spacious open-concept floor plan offers a large primary bedroom with an ensuite bath separately located from two other secondary bedrooms. The primary bathroom also includes dual sinks, a separate shower, and a large garden tub that is perfect for soaking. The Open Concept Kitchen overlooks the living and dining rooms making it perfect for family time and socializing with friends. Come see this lovely home now and make it your own!
